dct_title_s: Outline map of Deal Lake, Monmouth County, N.J. indicating restoration areas & recreational locations made for the Deal Lake Commission
dct_description_sm: A map outlining the areas surrounding Deal Lake in Monmouth County, including recreational areas as well as areas in need of restoration.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
This single map was originally part of a set of seven, per the inset label in the upper right corner.
